  <table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #dddddd;">
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center; padding: 10px 0;">
        <h2 style="color: #333333;">Reset Your DonorTrack Password</h2>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 20px 0; color: #555555;">
        <p>Hello <%= @user.email %>,</p>
        <p>We received a request to reset the password for your DonorTrack account, which you use to manage and track donations from your foundation. If you did make this request, please use the link below to reset your password:</p>
        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
          <%= link_to "Reset password", edit_identity_password_reset_url(sid: @signed_id), style: "background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;" %>
        </p>
        <p>For security reasons, this link will expire in <%= distance_of_time_in_words(Time.current, Time.current + @time_to_expire) %>. If it does expire, you can always request a new reset link from the DonorTrack login page.</p>
        <p>If you did not request this password reset, you can safely ignore this message. Your account will remain secure.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@donortrack.net" style="color: #007bff;">support@donortrack.net</a>.</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 10px 0; text-align: center; color: #aaaaaa; font-size: 12px;">
        <p>Best regards,<br>The DonorTrack Team</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
